    <p>
      But I’m not just the Capybara. As I crocheted a piece for a Multicultural Art Showcase, another side of me came to life: <strong>Bejeweled the Peacock</strong>—a nod to Taylor and a reflection of my glittery, chaotic, unapologetic heart.
    </p>
    <div class="callout">
      People who associate with a peacock come from a place of honor and integrity. They stand up for their beliefs and live by them. Flamboyant and true to themselves, they show their colors, walk their talk, and are entirely trustworthy and self-confident.
    </div>
    <p>
      Bejeweled is my reminder to shine without apology, speak my truth, and make art that sparkles.
    </p>
  </section>

